        <item>
            <title>勞工處將推「職安程式」新版，可匿名舉報工業安全問題</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=alert-from-larbour-department</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 08:33:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[勞工處]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220595</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>勞工處表示，最快將於今年首季推出新版本的應用程式，加入嚴重或致命工業意外發出的「職安警示」、「職安警示」動畫講解，以及舉報功能，讓用家可以用匿名形式投訴工業安全問題。</p><p>現時勞工處在發生嚴重或致命工業意外後，會在官方網站、應用程式及透過電郵發出現「職安警示」，提醒業界採取安全措施，以免再次發生同類型意外。</p><p>目前勞工處「職安警示」網上版可見，勞工處會提供意外日期、地點及意外摘要。同時勞工處會提供建議予擁有人、東主及僱主。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133220-431x580.jpg" alt="" width="431" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133220-431x580.jpg 431w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133220.jpg 669w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 431px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133236-431x580.jpg" alt="" width="431" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133236-431x580.jpg 431w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220133236.jpg 669w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 431px" /></p><p>勞工處官方網站亦有職安警示動畫。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220134157-601x580.jpg" alt="" width="601" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220134157-601x580.jpg 601w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240220134157.jpg 932w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 601px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708407543-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708407543-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/unwire-1708407543.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲勞工處有關「挖掘機的安全操作」的動畫影片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲勞工處有關「懸空式竹棚架拆卸」的動畫影片</p><div class="items_content"><div class="itemBody"><div class="itemFullText">勞工處副處長馮浩賢接受港台專訪時透露，最快今年第一季會提升「職安警示」內容及發放方式。勞工處已開始試行新應用程式。據港台引述勞工處表示，根據職安健法例，通常處方不會會公開調查結果，而工業傷亡權益會認為，政府應該公開全部嚴重職場意外調查結果，使業界可避免再次發生同類型慘案。</div></div></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/work_safety_alert.htm">勞工處</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1741019-20240220.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/">勞工處將推「職安程式」新版，可匿名舉報工業安全問題</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/20/alert-from-larbour-department/life-tech/smartcity/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
